snippet.title: Modern Classic Bodybuilders
channel_description:
Vintage Genetics stands for everything the golden era of bodybuilding was about.
Proportions, symmetry and overall body composition were of great importance when bodybuilding was in its golden days.

Here at VG we present you two bodybuilding brothers who both have the drive to be a true bodybuilder, a vintage bodybuilder. It's time to bring back the classic era that bodybuilding desperately needs again. 

After having won several competitions and being compared to classic physiques such as Arnold's, we find it important that the fruitful journey of bringing back classic bodybuilding will be presented on this channel.

Specific tips, knowledge and experience regarding training, eating and competing will be shared but also backstage footage, classic posing routines and contest preperations will be shown on this channel.

We hope to inspire other bodybuilders to join us in our quest to bring classic bodybuilders to the very top once again!

snippet.title: Shoulder Workout For BIG FULL Shoulders | Classic Bodybuilding
channel_description:
Vintage Genetics stands for everything the golden era of bodybuilding was about.
Proportions, symmetry and overall body composition were of great importance when bodybuilding was in its golden days.

Here at VG we present you two bodybuilding brothers who both have the drive to be a true bodybuilder, a vintage bodybuilder. It's time to bring back the classic era that bodybuilding desperately needs again. 

After having won several competitions and being compared to classic physiques such as Arnold's, we find it important that the fruitful journey of bringing back classic bodybuilding will be presented on this channel.

Specific tips, knowledge and experience regarding training, eating and competing will be shared but also backstage footage, classic posing routines and contest preperations will be shown on this channel.

We hope to inspire other bodybuilders to join us in our quest to bring classic bodybuilders to the very top once again!
